h1(#wxdirdialog). Wx::DirDialog

This class represents the directory chooser dialog.

h2. Derived from

"Dialog":dialog.html

"Window":window.html

"EvtHandler":evthandler.html

"Object":object.html

h2. Window styles



|@DD_DEFAULT_STYLE@|Equivalent to a combination of DEFAULT_DIALOG_STYLE, DD_NEW_DIR_BUTTON and RESIZE_BORDER (the last one is not used under WinCE).|
|@DD_NEW_DIR_BUTTON@|Add "Create newdirectory" button and allow directory names to be editable.  OnWindows the new directory button is only available with recentversions of the common dialogs.|


See also "Generic window styles":windowstyles.html.

